6520         /**
6521          * Wrapper of the function '_recognitionCallback', that is called, if the recongizer has finished processing.
6522          * @param {Array} List of identifier gestures that fits
6523          * @param {GeForMT.GestureRecognition.RecognitionContext} recognitionContext
6524          */
6525         recognitionCallback: function(identifierList, recognitionContext){
6526         
6527             _recognitionProcessManager._recognitionCallback(identifierList, recognitionContext);
6528         },
6529         /**
6530          * Function that is called, if the recongizer has finished processing.
6531          * @param {GeForMT.GestureRecognition.RecognitionContext} recognitionContext
6532          */
6533         _recognitionCallback: function(recognitionContext){
6534         
6535             //recognizedGestures is an object structure of following format: {gestureId => optionId, ..}
6536             var recognizedGestures = recognitionContext.recognizedGestures;
6537             var recognizedGesturesKeys = Object.keys(recognizedGestures);
6538             
6539             //console.debug("Recognized: " + recognizedGesturesKeys);
6540             if (recognizedGesturesKeys.length === 0) {
6541                 //recognition failed/ no gestures recognized!
6542                 _firstEventTimeStamp = null;
6543                 window.clearTimeout(_gestureContiguityIntervalTimer);
6544                 this.reset();
6545                 // create GestureRecognitionFailedEvent
6546                 var recognitionFailedEvent = new GestureRecognitionFailedEvent();
6547                 // notify listeners that recognition failed
6548                 var callbacks = GestureRecognitionEventListener.recognitionfailed;
6549                 for (var i = 0; i < callbacks.length; i++) {
6550                     callbacks[i](recognitionFailedEvent);
6551                 }
6552             }
6553             else {
6554                 //recognition succeed
6555                 
6556                 // create Feedback event about recognized candidates
6557                 var recognitionCandidatesEvent = new GestureRecognitionCandidatesEvent(recognizedGesturesKeys);
6558                 // notify listeners that recognition failed
6559                 var callbacks = GestureRecognitionEventListener.candidatesrecognized;
6560                 for (var k = 0; k < callbacks.length; k++) {
6561                     callbacks[k](recognitionCandidatesEvent);
6562                 }
6563                 
6564                 //reset list of noted gestures
6565                 this.recognizedGestures = [];
6566                 // notice gestures to exclude
6567                 var gesturesToExclude = [];
6568                 
6569                 for (var p = 0; p < this.priorities.length; p++) {
6570                     var pGestureId = this.priorities[p];
6571                     var exclude = true;
6572                     
6573                     for (var i = 0; i < recognizedGesturesKeys.length; i++) {
6574                         var rGestureId = recognizedGesturesKeys[i];
6575                         if (pGestureId == rGestureId) {
6576                         
6577                             exclude = false;
6578                             
6579                             // prepare gesture for further recognition steps
6580                             var model = recognitionContext.models[rGestureId];
6581                             
6582                             // get events of recognition context
6583                             var eventProfile = recognitionContext.eventProfiles[rGestureId];
6584                             var gesturePathes = recognitionContext.gesturePathes[rGestureId];
6585                             var events = this.eventProfilesHistory[pGestureId].slice();
6586                             events.push(eventProfile);
6587                             var pathes = this.gesturePathesHistory[rGestureId].slice();
6588                             pathes.push(gesturePathes);
6589                             // console.debug(model.model.isMultistrokeGesture);
6590                             
6591                             if (!model.online) {
6592                                 // save history
6593                                 this.eventProfilesHistory[rGestureId].push(eventProfile);
6594                                 // delete checked events from event profile
6595                                 this.eventProfiles[rGestureId] = [];
6596                                 
6597                                 this.gesturePathesHistory[rGestureId].push(gesturePathes);
6598                                 // delete checked gesturePathes
6599                                 this.gesturePathes[rGestureId] = [];
6600                                 
6601                                 // all subtasks of one option processed?
6602                                 if (recognitionContext.checkmodels[rGestureId].oneOptionProcessedSuccessfully()) {
6603                                     //more than one candidate --> wait for next input
6604                                     if (recognizedGesturesKeys.length > 1) {
6605                                     
6606                                         var gestureRecognizedEvent = new GestureRecognizedEvent(pGestureId, model, events, pathes);
6607                                         
6608                                         this.recognizedGestures.push(gestureRecognizedEvent);
6609                                         
6610                                     }
6611                                     else 
6612                                         if (recognizedGesturesKeys.length == 1) {
6613                                             // create gesture recognized event and handle it to application layer
6614                                             // unambiguous gesture recognized
6615                                             this.gestureRecognized(rGestureId, events, pathes);
6616                                         }
6617                                     
6618                                     exclude = true;
6619                                 }
6620                                 
6621                             }
6622                             else {
6623                                 // online recognition
6624                                 
6625                                 this.gestureRecognized(rGestureId, events);
6626                                 exclude = true;
6627                                 
6628                             }
6629                         }
6630                         
6631                     }
6632                     if (exclude && !this.online) {
6633                         gesturesToExclude.push(pGestureId);
6634                     }
6635                 }
6636                 // remove this gestures saved in from gesturesToExclude list,
6637                 // because recognition failed
6638                 for (var j = 0; j < gesturesToExclude.length; j++) {
6639                     this.excludeGestureFromRecognition(gesturesToExclude[j]);
6640                 }
6641                 
6642             }
6643         }
6644     };
6645     /**
6646      * Recognition processor component. Recognizes a gesture with its adapted
6647      * strategies for GeForMT gesture recognition.
6648      * @namespace
6649      */
6650     var Recognizer = (function(){
6651     
6652         /**
6653          * Recognizes the relation between gesture pathes.
6654          * @class
6655          */
6656         function RelationRecognizer(){
6657         
6658         }
6659         RelationRecognizer.prototype = /*lends*/ {
6660             /**
6661              * Tolerance threshold for CONNECT relations. (px)
6662              * @type Number
6663              * @default 25
6664              */
6665             connectTolerance: 25,
6666             /**
6667              * Offset of horizontal range for AMONG relation. (px)
6668              * @type Number
6669              * @default 30
6670              */
6671             horizontalLimitOffset: 30,
6672             /**
6673              * Offset of vertical range for ASIDE relation. (px)
6674              * @type Number
6675              * @default 20
6676              */
6677             verticalLimitOffset: 20,
6678             /**
6679              * Offset representing the valid area for SYNC relation. (px)
6680              * @type Number
6681              * @default 10
6682              */
6683             synchroThreshold: 10,
6684             /**
6685              * Offset representing the minimal average distance to recognize a SPLIT or JOIN relationship.
6686              * @type Number
6687              * @default: 25
6688              */
6689             minDistanceOffset: 25,
6690             /**
6691              * Recognize parameters in time and space to check relations between
6692              * gesture. Implemented relation types are: CROSS, SPLIT, JOIN, ASIDE, AMONG, CONNECT_START and CONNECT_END.
6693              *
6694              * @param {Object}
6695              *            gesturePathes
6696              * @param {Object}
6697              *            gesturePathesHistory
6698              * @param {Object}
6699              *            relationCheckContext Object of following format:
6700              *            (gestureId => (relation => relationType of type
6701              *            GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES, option => optionIndex, isMultistroke=> true/false, isMultitouch => true/false))
6702              * @return {Object} Structure: (gestureId => optionIndex)
6703              */
6704             recognize: function(gesturePathes, gesturePathesHistory, relationCheckContext){
6705                 var gesturesKeys = Object.keys(relationCheckContext);
6706                 var result = {};
6707                 for (var i = 0; i < gesturesKeys.length; i++) {
6708                     var gestureId = gesturesKeys[i];
6709                     var relation = relationCheckContext[gestureId].relation;
6710                     var optionIndex = relationCheckContext[gestureId].option;
6711                     var templates = gesturePathes[gestureId];
6712                     var previousStrokeTemplates = gesturePathesHistory[gestureId][gesturePathesHistory[gestureId].length - 1];
6713                     var templateCollection = templates.concat(previousStrokeTemplates);
6714                     var isMultistroke = relationCheckContext[gestureId].isMultistroke;
6715                     var isMultitouch = relationCheckContext[gestureId].isMultitouch;
6716                     var relationRecognized = false;
6717                     switch (relation) {
6718                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.CROSS:
6719                             if (isMultistroke &&
6720                             typeof previousStrokeTemplates !== 'undefined' &&
6721                             previousStrokeTemplates.length > 0) {
6722                                 var ptPoints = previousStrokeTemplates[0].points;
6723                                 var tPoints = templates[0].points;
6724                                 var pointsOfIntersection = [];
6725                                 for (var pt = 0; pt < ptPoints.length - 1; pt++) {
6726                                     var x1 = ptPoints[pt].x;
6727                                     var x2 = ptPoints[pt + 1].x;
6728                                     var y1 = ptPoints[pt].y;
6729                                     var y2 = ptPoints[pt + 1].y;
6730                                     var pBoundingBox = this._getBoundingBox(x1, x2, y1, y2);
6731                                     if (relationRecognized) {
6732                                         break;
6733                                     }
6734                                     for (var t = 0; t < tPoints.length - 1; t++) {
6735                                         var xt1 = tPoints[t].x;
6736                                         var xt2 = tPoints[t + 1].x;
6737                                         var yt1 = tPoints[t].y;
6738                                         var yt2 = tPoints[t + 1].y;
6739                                         var tBoundingBox = this._getBoundingBox(xt1, xt2, yt1, yt2);
6740                                         var intersectionBoundingBox = this._getIntersectionBoundingBox(pBoundingBox, tBoundingBox);
6741                                         if (intersectionBoundingBox !== null) {
6742                                         
6743                                             //calculate parameters of linear functions
6744                                             var linearFunc1 = this._calcLinearFunction(x1, y1, x2, y2);
6745                                             var linearFunc2 = this._calcLinearFunction(xt1, yt1, xt2, yt2);
6746                                             // calculate point of intersection
6747                                             var pointOfIntersection = this._calcPointOfIntersection(linearFunc1, linearFunc2);
6748                                             
6749                                             // point of intersection in valid range?
6750                                             // if true, then pathes are crossing
6751                                             var poiX = pointOfIntersection.x;
6752                                             var poiY = pointOfIntersection.y;
6753                                             if (!isNaN(poiX) && !isNaN(poiY)) {
6754                                             
6755                                                 if (poiY >= intersectionBoundingBox.top &&
6756                                                 poiY <= intersectionBoundingBox.bottom &&
6757                                                 poiX >= intersectionBoundingBox.left &&
6758                                                 poiX <= intersectionBoundingBox.right) {
6759                                                     //part of pathes are crossing
6760                                                     relationRecognized = true;
6761                                                     break;
6762                                                 // pointsOfIntersection.push(pointOfIntersection);
6763                                                 }
6764                                             }
6765                                         }
6766                                     }
6767                                     
6768                                 }
6769                                 
6770                             }
6771                             else {
6772                                 if (!isMultistroke) {
6773                                 
6774                                 }
6775                                 relationRecognized = true;
6776                             }
6777                             break;
6778                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.JOIN:
6779                             if (typeof templates !== 'undefined' &&
6780                             templates.length > 1 &&
6781                             isMultitouch) {
6782                                 var deltaBeginX = templates[0].points[0].x - templates[templates.length - 1].points[0].x;
6783                                 var deltaEndX = templates[0].points[templates[0].points.length - 1].x - templates[templates.length - 1].points[templates[templates.length - 1].points.length - 1].x;
6784                                 var deltaBeginY = templates[0].points[0].y - templates[templates.length - 1].points[0].y;
6785                                 var deltaEndY = templates[0].points[templates[0].points.length - 1].y - templates[templates.length - 1].points[templates[templates.length - 1].points.length - 1].y;
6786                                 var distanceAtBeginning = Math.sqrt(deltaBeginX * deltaBeginX + deltaBeginY * deltaBeginY);
6787                                 var distanceAtEnd = Math.sqrt(deltaEndX * deltaEndX + deltaEndY * deltaEndY);
6788                                 if (distanceAtBeginning > distanceAtEnd && Math.abs(distanceAtBeginning - distanceAtEnd) > this.minDistanceOffset) {
6789                                     relationRecognized = true;
6790                                 }
6791                                 else {
6792                                     relationRecognized = false;
6793                                 }
6794                                 
6795                             }
6796                             else {
6797                                 relationRecognized = true;
6798                             }
6799                             break;
6800                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.SYNC:
6801                             if (typeof templates !== 'undefined' &&
6802                             templates.length > 1 &&
6803                             isMultitouch) {
6804                                 //resample points
6805                                 var resampledPathes = [];
6806                                 var n = 6;
6807                                 for (var t = 0; t < templates.length; t++) {
6808                                     var newPoints = this._resample(templates[t].points, n);
6809                                     resampledPathes.push(newPoints);
6810                                 }
6811                                 
6812                                 //calculate distances between points
6813                                 var avgDistances = [];
6814                                 for (var pi = 0; pi < n; pi++) {
6815                                     //check point i of n
6816                                     for (var rp = 1; rp < resampledPathes.length; rp++) {
6817                                         if (typeof avgDistances[pi] == 'undefined') {
6818                                             avgDistances[pi] = this._distance(resampledPathes[0][pi], resampledPathes[rp][pi]);
6819                                         }
6820                                         else {
6821                                             avgDistances[pi] = avgDistances[pi] + this._distance(resampledPathes[0][pi], resampledPathes[rp][pi]);
6822                                         }
6823                                     }
6824                                     avgDistances[pi] = avgDistances[pi] / (resampledPathes.length - 1);
6825                                     //check for almost constant distances
6826                                     console.debug(Math.abs(avgDistances[0] - avgDistances[pi]));
6827                                     if (avgDistances.length > 1 && Math.abs(avgDistances[0] - avgDistances[pi]) > this.synchroThreshold) {
6828                                         relationRecognized = false;
6829                                         break;
6830                                     }
6831                                     else {
6832                                         relationRecognized = true;
6833                                     }
6834                                 }
6835                                 console.debug(relationRecognized);
6836                             }
6837                             relationRecognized = true;
6838                             break;
6839                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.SPLIT:
6840                             if (typeof templates !== 'undefined' &&
6841                             templates.length > 1 &&
6842                             isMultitouch) {
6843                             
6844                                 var deltaBeginX = templates[0].points[0].x - templates[templates.length - 1].points[0].x;
6845                                 var deltaEndX = templates[0].points[templates[0].points.length - 1].x - templates[templates.length - 1].points[templates[templates.length - 1].points.length - 1].x;
6846                                 var deltaBeginY = templates[0].points[0].y - templates[templates.length - 1].points[0].y;
6847                                 var deltaEndY = templates[0].points[templates[0].points.length - 1].y - templates[templates.length - 1].points[templates[templates.length - 1].points.length - 1].y;
6848                                 
6849                                 var distanceAtBeginning = Math.sqrt(deltaBeginX * deltaBeginX + deltaBeginY * deltaBeginY);
6850                                 var distanceAtEnd = Math.sqrt(deltaEndX * deltaEndX + deltaEndY * deltaEndY);
6851                                 if (distanceAtBeginning < distanceAtEnd && Math.abs(distanceAtBeginning - distanceAtEnd) > this.minDistanceOffset) {
6852                                     relationRecognized = true;
6853                                 }
6854                                 else {
6855                                     relationRecognized = false;
6856                                 }
6857                                 
6858                             }
6859                             else {
6860                                 relationRecognized = true;
6861                             }
6862                             break;
6863                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.CONNECT_START:
6864                             if (typeof previousStrokeTemplates !== 'undefined' &&
6865                             previousStrokeTemplates.length > 0 &&
6866                             isMultistroke) {
6867                                 //previous stroke pathes
6868                                 var refX = 0;
6869                                 var refY = 0;
6870                                 for (var pcst = 0; pcst < previousStrokeTemplates.length; pcst++) {
6871                                     refX += previousStrokeTemplates[pcst].points[0].x;
6872                                     refY += previousStrokeTemplates[pcst].points[0].y;
6873                                 }
6874                                 refX = refX / previousStrokeTemplates.length;
6875                                 refY = refY / previousStrokeTemplates.length;
6876                                 
6877                                 // current stroke pathes
6878                                 var x = 0;
6879                                 var y = 0;
6880                                 for (var cst = 0; cst < templates.length; cst++) {
6881                                     x += templates[cst].points[0].x;
6882                                     y += templates[cst].points[0].y;
6883                                 }
6884                                 x = x / templates.length;
6885                                 y = y / templates.length;
6886                                 
6887                                 var isConnected = true;
6888                                 
6889                                 var dx = refX - x;
6890                                 var dy = refY - y;
6891                                 var a = Math.sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy);
6892                                 if (a < this.connectTolerance) {
6893                                     relationRecognized = true;
6894                                 }
6895                                 else {
6896                                     relationRecognized = false;
6897                                 }
6898                                 
6899                             }
6900                             else {
6901                                 relationRecognized = true;
6902                             }
6903                             break;
6904                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.CONNECT_END:
6905                             if (typeof previousStrokeTemplates !== 'undefined' &&
6906                             previousStrokeTemplates.length > 0 &&
6907                             isMultistroke) {
6908                                 // previous stroke pathes
6909                                 var refX = 0;
6910                                 var refY = 0;
6911                                 for (var pcet = 0; pcet < previousStrokeTemplates.length; pcet++) {
6912                                     var strokeLength = previousStrokeTemplates[pcet].points.length;
6913                                     refX += previousStrokeTemplates[pcet].points[strokeLength - 1].x;
6914                                     refY += previousStrokeTemplates[pcet].points[strokeLength - 1].y;
6915                                 }
6916                                 refX = refX / previousStrokeTemplates.length;
6917                                 refY = refY / previousStrokeTemplates.length;
6918                                 // current stroke pathes
6919                                 var x = 0;
6920                                 var y = 0;
6921                                 for (var cet = 0; cet < templates.length; cet++) {
6922                                     x += templates[cet].points[0].x;
6923                                     y += templates[cet].points[0].y;
6924                                 }
6925                                 x = x / templates.length;
6926                                 y = y / templates.length;
6927                                 
6928                                 var isConnected = true;
6929                                 
6930                                 var dx = refX - x;
6931                                 var dy = refY - y;
6932                                 var a = Math.sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy);
6933                                 if (a < this.connectTolerance) {
6934                                     relationRecognized = true;
6935                                 }
6936                                 else {
6937                                     relationRecognized = false;
6938                                 }
6939                                 
6940                             }
6941                             else {
6942                                 //recognize this relation in next recognition step
6943                                 relationRecognized = true;
6944                             }
6945                             break;
6946                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.AMONG:
6947                             if (typeof previousStrokeTemplates !== 'undefined' &&
6948                             previousStrokeTemplates.length > 0 &&
6949                             isMultistroke) {
6950                                 var minX = +Infinity;
6951                                 var maxX = 0;
6952                                 var minY = +Infinity;
6953                                 var maxY = 0;
6954                                 // calc bounding box
6955                                 for (var pta = 0; pta < previousStrokeTemplates.length; pta++) {
6956                                     var points = previousStrokeTemplates[pta].points;
6957                                     for (var p = 0; p < points.length; p++) {
6958                                         var x = points[p].x;
6959                                         var y = points[p].y;
6960                                         if (x < minX) {
6961                                             minX = x;
6962                                         }
6963                                         if (y < minY) {
6964                                             minY = y;
6965                                         }
6966                                         if (x > maxX) {
6967                                             maxX = x;
6968                                         }
6969                                         if (y > maxY) {
6970                                             maxY = y;
6971                                         }
6972                                     }
6973                                 }
6974                                 
6975                                 //offset for tolerance
6976                                 minX = minX - this.horizontalLimitOffset;
6977                                 maxX = maxX + this.horizontalLimitOffset;
6978                                 relationRecognized = true;
6979                                 // check current added gesture strokes
6980                                 for (var t = 0; t < templates.length; t++) {
6981                                     var template = templates[t];
6982                                     for (var tp = 0; tp < template.points.length; tp++) {
6983                                         var px = template.points[tp].x;
6984                                         var py = template.points[tp].y;
6985                                         var pointInValidRange = (px > minX &&
6986                                         px < maxX &&
6987                                         py < minY ||
6988                                         py > maxY);
6989                                         if (!pointInValidRange) {
6990                                             relationRecognized = false;
6991                                             break;
6992                                         }
6993                                     }
6994                                 }
6995                             }
6996                             else {
6997                                 //recognize this relation in next recognition step
6998                                 relationRecognized = true;
6999                             }
7000                             break;
7001                         case GeForMT.RELATION_TYPES.ASIDE:
7002                             if (typeof previousStrokeTemplates !== 'undefined' &&
7003                             previousStrokeTemplates.length > 0 &&
7004                             isMultistroke) {
7005                                 var minX = +Infinity;
7006                                 var maxX = 0;
7007                                 var minY = +Infinity;
7008                                 var maxY = 0;
7009                                 
7010                                 // calc bounding box
7011                                 for (var pta = 0; pta < previousStrokeTemplates.length; pta++) {
7012                                     var points = previousStrokeTemplates[pta].points;
7013                                     for (var p = 0; p < points.length; p++) {
7014                                         var x = points[p].x;
7015                                         var y = points[p].y;
7016                                         if (x < minX) {
7017                                             minX = x;
7018                                         }
7019                                         if (y < minY) {
7020                                             minY = y;
7021                                         }
7022                                         if (x > maxX) {
7023                                             maxX = x;
7024                                         }
7025                                         if (y > maxY) {
7026                                             maxY = y;
7027                                         }
7028                                     }
7029                                 }
7030                                 
7031                                 //offset for tolerance
7032                                 minY = minY - this.verticalLimitOffset;
7033                                 maxY = maxY + this.verticalLimitOffset;
7034                                 relationRecognized = true;
7035                                 // check current added gesture strokes
7036                                 for (var t = 0; t < templates.length; t++) {
7037                                     var template = templates[t];
7038                                     for (var tp = 0; tp < template.points.length; tp++) {
7039                                         var px = template.points[tp].x;
7040                                         var py = template.points[tp].y;
7041                                         var pointInValidRange = (px < minX ||
7042                                         px > maxX &&
7043                                         py > minY &&
7044                                         py < maxY);
7045                                         if (!pointInValidRange) {
7046                                             relationRecognized = false;
7047                                             break;
7048                                         }
7049                                     }
7050                                 }
7051                             }
7052                             else {
7053                                 //recognize this relation in next recognition step
7054                                 relationRecognized = true;
7055                             }
7056                             break;
7057                     }
7058                     if (relationRecognized) {
7059                         result[gestureId] = optionIndex;
7060                     }
7061                 }
7062                 return result;
7063             },
7064             /**
7065              * Helper method to calculate the bounding box (a rectangle) based on two points.
7066              * @param {Number} x1
7067              * @param {Number} x2
7068              * @param {Number} y1
7069              * @param {Number} y2
7070              * @return {Objects} Object that represents the bounding box. It has the following properties: top, right, left and bottom.
7071              */
7072             _getBoundingBox: function(x1, x2, y1, y2){
7073                 var top = Math.min(y1, y2);
7074                 var right = Math.max(x1, x2);
7075                 var bottom = Math.max(y1, y2);
7076                 var left = Math.min(x1, x2);
7077                 return {
7078                     top: top,
7079                     right: right,
7080                     bottom: bottom,
7081                     left: left
7082                 };
7083             },
7084             /**
7085              * Helper method to calculate intersection area of two bounding boxes (rectangles).
7086              * @param {Object} boundingBox1
7087              * @param {Object} boundingBox2
7088              * @return {Objects} Object that represents the intersection area. It has the following properties: top, right, left and bottom.
7089              */
7090             _getIntersectionBoundingBox: function(boundingBox1, boundingBox2){
7091                 var top = Math.max(boundingBox1.top, boundingBox2.top);
7092                 var bottom = Math.min(boundingBox1.bottom, boundingBox2.bottom);
7093                 var right = Math.min(boundingBox1.right, boundingBox2.right);
7094                 var left = Math.max(boundingBox1.left, boundingBox2.left);
7095                 
7096                 if (top > bottom || left > right) {
7097                     return null;
7098                 }
7099                 return {
7100                     top: top,
7101                     right: right,
7102                     bottom: bottom,
7103                     left: left
7104                 };
7105             },
7106             /**
7107              * Helper method that calculates main parameter of a linear function based on two points.
7108              * @param {Number} x1
7109              * @param {Number} y1
7110              * @param {Number} x2
7111              * @param {Number} y2
7112              * @return Object containing 'gradient' and 'offset' that represents the main parameter of a line.
7113              */
7114             _calcLinearFunction: function(x1, y1, x2, y2){
7115             
7116                 var m = (y2 - y1) / (x2 - x1);
7117                 var b = y2 - x2 * m;
7118                 return {
7119                     gradient: m,
7120                     offset: b
7121                 };
7122             },
7123             /**
7124              * Calculates the point of intersection of two linear functions.
7125              * @param {Object} linearContext1 Parameter of first linear function.
7126              * @param {Object} linearContext2 Parameter of second linear function.
7127              * @return Object point of intersection represented by x and y coordiante.
7128              */
7129             _calcPointOfIntersection: function(linearContext1, linearContext2){
7130                 var poiX = (linearContext2.offset - linearContext1.offset) /
7131                 (linearContext1.gradient - linearContext2.gradient);
7132                 var poiY = linearContext1.gradient * poiX +
7133                 linearContext1.offset;
7134                 return {
7135                     x: poiX,
7136                     y: poiY
7137                 };
7138             },
7139             /**
7140              * Resample performed gesture pathes.
7141              * @param {Array} points List of points.
7142              * @param {Number} n Number of points
7143              * @return {Array} Resampled points
7144              */
7145             _resample: function(points, n){
7146             
7147                 var I = this._pathLength(points) / (n - 1); // interval length
7148                 var D = 0.0;
7149                 var newpoints = [points[0]];
7150                 
7151                 for (var i = 1; i < points.length; i++) {
7152                 
7153                     var d = this._distance(points[i - 1], points[i]);
7154                     
7155                     if ((D + d) >= I) {
7156                         var qx = points[i - 1].x +
7157                         ((I - D) / d) *
7158                         (points[i].x - points[i - 1].x);
7159                         
7160                         var qy = points[i - 1].y +
7161                         ((I - D) / d) *
7162                         (points[i].y - points[i - 1].y);
7163                         var q = {
7164                             x: qx,
7165                             y: qy
7166                         };
7167                         newpoints[newpoints.length] = q; // append new point
7168                         // 'q'
7169                         points.splice(i, 0, q); // insert 'q' at position i in
7170                         // points s.t. 'q' will be the next
7171                         // i
7172                         D = 0.0;
7173                         
7174                     }
7175                     else {
7176                         D += d;
7177                     }
7178                 }
7179                 return newpoints;
7180             },
7181             /**
7182              * Calculate distance between two points.
7183              * @param {GeForMT.Templatebuilder.Point} p1 First point.
7184              * @param {GeForMT.Templatebuilder.Point} p1 Second point.
7185              * @return {Number} Distance between points.
7186              */
7187             _distance: function(p1, p2){
7188                 var dx = p2.x - p1.x;
7189                 var dy = p2.y - p1.y;
7190                 return Math.sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy);
7191             },
7192             /**
7193              * Calculate path length.
7194              * @param {Array} points
7195              * @return {Number} Path length.
7196              */
7197             _pathLength: function(points){
7198                 var d = 0.0;
7199                 for (var i = 1; i < points.length; i++) {
7200                     d += this._distance(points[i - 1], points[i]);
7201                 }
7202                 return d;
7203             }
7204             
7205         };

7207         /**
7208          * StaticGestureRecognizer Recognizes static gestures like POINT. In
7209          * this version only simple POINT gestures are implemented!
7210          * @class
7211          */
7212         function StaticGestureRecognizer(){
7213         
7214         }
7215         
7216         StaticGestureRecognizer.prototype = /*@lends*/ {
7217         
7218             /**
7219              * Maximum of movement range, where a point gesture can bee recognized.
7220              * @type Number
7221              * @default 10
7222              */
7223             movementRadius: 10,
7224             /**
7225              * Main function to compare performed gestures and candidate gestures.
7226              * @param {Object} performedGestures
7227              * @param {Object} candidateGestures
7228              * @return {Object} Structure: (gestureId => optionIndex)
7229              */
7230             recognize: function(performedGestures, candidateGestures){
7231                 var candidateGestureKeys = Object.keys(candidateGestures);
7232                 var result = {};
7233                 for (var i = 0; i < candidateGestureKeys.length; i++) {
7234                 
7235                     var candidateId = candidateGestureKeys[i];
7236                     var candidate = candidateGestures[candidateId];
7237                     var optionKeys = Object.keys(candidate);
7238                     var options = candidateGestures[candidateId];
7239                     var templates = performedGestures[candidateId]; // check for
7240                     // simultanous
7241                     // contacts
7242                     for (var o = 0; o < optionKeys.length; o++) {
7243                         var atomicGestures = options[optionKeys[o]];
7244                         var optionRecognized = false;
7245                         for (var t = 0; t < templates.length; t++) {
7246                             // single contact
7247                             var points = templates[t].points;
7248                             var events = templates[t].events;
7249                             var dx = points[points.length - 1].x - points[0].x;
7250                             var dy = points[points.length - 1].y - points[0].y;
7251                             var movementDistance = Math.sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy);
7252                             if (movementDistance < this.movementRadius && atomicGestures[0].gestureType == GeForMT.CONTACT_TYPES.POINT) {
7253                                 // POINT recognized
7254                                 optionRecognized = true;
7255                             }
7256                             else {
7257                                 optionRecognized = false;
7258                                 // case MOVE gesture definition
7259                                 if (atomicGestures[0].gestureType == GeForMT.CONTACT_TYPES.MOVE) {
7260                                     optionRecognized = true;
7261                                 }
7262                                 break;
7263                             }
7264                         }
7265                         if (optionRecognized) {
7266                             result[candidateId] = {};
7267                             result[candidateId] = parseInt(optionKeys[o]);
7268                             break;
7269                         }
7270                     }
7271                 }
7272                 return result;
7273             }
7274         };
